summary: Hi.  Ok. So, I'm relatively new in the fandom and all I've read in posts and fanfictions is Top!Crowley. I mean, did the fandom...
question: Hi.  Ok. So, I'm relatively new in the fandom and all I've read in posts and fanfictions is Top!Crowley. I mean, did the fandom just decide that Crowley never tops? Is there something I'm missing? Not that I mind it's just that I've never seen the lack of a character topping to this extent.
answer:
well i can’t say much since im relatively new to the fandom too (i joined last year, somewhere around september i think?) but maybe casting david tennant as crowley had a strong and almost instant impact?

i mean almost all of the older fanfic I’ve read had crowley being way more confident, aggressive, edgy and yes, a top, than the newer ones I’ve read. it’s weird, really.

really the best thing you can do if you want to get to the bottom (AH!) of this is ask an older member of the fandom like maggie or hallie.

good luck on your “research” and welcome btw!!
